    <item>
      <title>美国法院推翻美国证券交易委员会对冲基金费用披露规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/sec-private-fund-fee-disclosure-rules-struck-down-by-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦上诉法院推翻了美国证券交易委员会要求对冲基金和私募股权公司向投资者详细说明季度费用和支出的规定 — — 这是监管机构对私募基金行业的打击遭遇的重大挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-05/sec-private-fund-fee-disclosure-rules-struck-down-by-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 05 Jun 2024 13:36:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
